  m_text: 'CONCLUSION


    In this experiment, we learnt that-


    Glass tubes
    and rods can be cut to reduce it to a particular length.


    A triangular file
    is used to make a deep scratch on the glass tube, and then it is broken by applying 
    pressure on both of its sides.


    The jagged edges of the cut tube can be
    trimmed using a wire gauze.


    The method of fire polishing is used to round
    the edges of the glass tube.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 356b1ee212a194b49bed1adb63017c1b, type: 2}
